        {
            "title": "GameStop預計本月競購eBay;股價飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6FUYRqCmnedqp5eVoAun.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7I0KO_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"GameStop\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:GameStop;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/GameStop\">GameStop</a> Corp (NYSE:GME)股價在週五盤後交易中躍升逾4%,此前有報導稱這家零售商正準備向電商巨頭<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"eBay\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:eBay;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/eBay\">eBay</a> Inc (NASDAQ:EBAY)提出正式收購要約。這一消息也推動<span><span><span><span>eBay</span></span></span></span>股價攀升逾12%,投資者正在消化這筆將把實體零售商與全球最大線上二手市場結合在一起的交易。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據《華爾街日報》報導,執行長Ryan Cohen將此交易視為戰略轉型的一部分,旨在將GameStop打造成市值超過1000億美元的零售巨頭。知情人士透露,該公司在提出潛在收購要約之前,一直在悄悄建倉eBay股票。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4f86162a-4c02-360e-b05c-17565f909586-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">擬議中的合併可能將聚焦於GameStop近期向高端收藏品和遊戲紀念品的轉型。這一策略與eBay現有平台相契合,後者仍是二手市場收藏品和稀有商品的主要全球樞紐。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">GameStop目前市值約120億美元,正在追求一個規模數倍於自身的收購目標。eBay的市值約為460億美元,不過截至3月,GameStop已用近90億美元的現金儲備強化了其資產負債表。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">正式收購要約可能最早於本月稍後提交給eBay董事會。如果這家電商公司的領導層不予接受,Cohen可能選擇直接向eBay股東提出收購。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一消息傳出之際,Cohen的薪酬方案最近已作出調整,為這種轉型提供巨額激勵。據先前報導,如果公司市值達到1000億美元的里程碑,他將獲得高達350億美元的股票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位執行長此前在1月下旬向《華爾街日報》表示,他正在積極尋找潛在的交易目標。他特別強調在消費和零售板塊的擴張,以推動品牌遠超其核心電子遊戲業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場參與者目前正密切關注eBay董事會的正式回應。若出現委託書爭奪戰,Cohen預計將利用其龐大的線上追隨者群體為這筆交易爭取支持。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/gamestop%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BCebay-%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-224639848.html",
